Author: zombeezinthetrap
Text: Fainting is never good sign at any bmi. Make sure you are getting electrolytes. Drink a Gatorade and eat a banana. Try to be gentle with yourself and eat something. Even if you have been binging the past few days, your body still needs fuel daily. :)
